data.description: Expansive 3-bed, 3-bath home on 2 acres of serene landscape. Over 2000 sqft, featuring a new roof in 2021. Perfect for RV enthusiasts with a hookup. Step into the updated kitchen with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. Enjoy family meals in the spacious eat-in kitchen. The master suite is a retreat with a jetted tub, separate shower, and a roomy walk-in closet. A sunroom adds to the charm and provides a perfect spot to relax. The laundry room boasts built-in cabinets. The backyard is a haven with a new pergola, and beautiful landscaping. This property is not in a flood zone and qualifies for rural development. Your spacious dream home awaits! Call your favorite realtor for a showing today!
